4. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The use of deep neural networks for classification and filtering of candidates also falls under the domain of machine learning. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics): Building height estimation is an important problem in robotics for navigation and mapping, hence this sub-category is also a possibility.
